    "statementHTML": "<div class=\"statement-body\">\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-goal\">\n   <h2><span class=\"icon icon-goal\">&nbsp;</span><span>Goal </span></h2>\n   <span class=\"question-statement\">The <strong>Collatz conjecture</strong> is one of the most famous unsolved problems in mathematics. The conjecture states that for any positive integer, its Collatz sequence (defined below) converges to <const>1</const>.<br><br>You are given a list of integers, and you must compute the <strong>total stopping time</strong> (ie. steps before reaching <const>1</const>) and the <strong>maximum reached</strong> in the Collatz sequence of that number.<br><br><strong>Mathematical information</strong><br>The sequence is defined as such:<br>Given a strictly positive integer <var>n</var>,<br>If <var>n</var> is even, the next term is <var>n</var>/2<br>If <var>n</var> is odd, the next term is 3*<var>n</var>+1</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-protocol\">\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-input\"><strong>Line 1</strong> An integer <var>Q</var> representing the amount of integers to process<br><strong>Next <var>Q</var> lines:</strong> <var>n</var>, a positive integer to process</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-output\"><strong><var>Q</var> lines:</strong> The total stopping time and maximum reached for the Collatz sequence of the number, separated by a space</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Constraints</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-constraints\">1 &lt;= <var>Q</var> &lt;= 50<br>0 &lt; <var>n</var> &lt; 10,000,000</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Example</div>\n      <div class=\"statement-inout\">\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-in\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-in\">3\n5\n10\n12</pre>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-out\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-out\">5 16\n6 16\n9 16</pre>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n   </div>\n</div>"
